Oysters...

1080
02:21:45.352 --> 02:21:48.743
and beautiful pink pearls.

1081
02:21:49.432 --> 02:21:53.982
From the blue seas
and silver rivers of Britain.

1082
02:21:57.268 --> 02:22:01.165
Gained from the green forests...

1083
02:22:01.873 --> 02:22:04.648
and golden ponds of Britain...

1084
02:22:05.659 --> 02:22:10.315
wild pheasants, lovesome geese.

1085
02:22:27.383 --> 02:22:28.815
Cowards.

1086
02:22:34.188 --> 02:22:37.394
Crawl! Crawl! Crawl!

1087
02:22:37.893 --> 02:22:40.273
I hate them!

1088
02:22:47.588 --> 02:22:49.357
Almighty Caesar says...

1089
02:22:50.290 --> 02:22:52.428
to balance the state budget

1090
02:22:52.508 --> 02:22:55.315
we shall confiscate
the entire estates...

1091
02:22:55.435 --> 02:22:57.653
of all those who have failed Rome.

1092
02:23:02.248 --> 02:23:04.740
Read out your list, Longinus.

1093
02:23:06.926 --> 02:23:08.656
Senators Galva...

1094
02:23:09.670 --> 02:23:11.224
Aponius...

1095
02:23:11.304 --> 02:23:12.597
Marcellus...

1096
02:23:13.133 --> 02:23:14.341
Antonius...

1097
02:23:15.149 --> 02:23:16.163
Cassius...

1098
02:23:16.785 --> 02:23:17.461
Chaerea...

1099
02:23:18.462 --> 02:23:21.273
They have failed me. Arrest them.

1100
02:23:21.393 --> 02:23:22.540
Lepidus...

1101
02:23:24.652 --> 02:23:27.130
Sextus and Octavius.

1102
02:23:27.637 --> 02:23:28.648
Guards, arrest them.

1103
02:23:46.469 --> 02:23:48.588
Almighty Caesar says...

1104
02:23:48.668 --> 02:23:50.357
finish your dinner.

1105
02:23:53.143 --> 02:23:53.940
Eat!

1106
02:24:02.246 --> 02:24:03.523
He must be done soon.

1107
02:24:09.148 --> 02:24:10.563
Watch Chaerea.

1108
02:24:11.389 --> 02:24:12.140
Why?

1109
02:24:12.593 --> 02:24:14.232
The omens are not good.

1110
02:24:14.871 --> 02:24:16.330
Be on your guard.

1111
02:24:18.572 --> 02:24:21.226
I think he intends to kill me.

1112
02:24:26.207 --> 02:24:27.607
What is amusing, Caesar?

1113
02:24:29.130 --> 02:24:30.590
Just a thought.

1114
02:24:30.670 --> 02:24:33.440
May I ask what thought?

1115
02:24:37.203 --> 02:24:40.023
Is it true that there's a conspiracy
against me, Longinus?

1116
02:24:40.747 --> 02:24:43.398
Well, lord... that is... I mean...

1117
02:24:43.953 --> 02:24:46.629
It seems there is a secret plot.

1118
02:24:46.709 --> 02:24:49.148
A plot is always a secret, if it's not
a secret, it's not a plot but a plan.

1119
02:24:49.228 --> 02:24:51.319
That is logical, is it not, Claudius?

1120
02:24:51.399 --> 02:24:53.499
Even a half-wit can know that
and you're a half-wit.

1121
02:24:53.579 --> 02:24:55.683
Half of me is, Caesar.

1122
02:24:58.671 --> 02:25:00.744
The situation's gone too far.

1123
02:25:00.824 --> 02:25:02.841
He has mocked the guards,
overruled the government

1124
02:25:02.921 --> 02:25:04.857
and insulted
the best families in Rome.

1125
02:25:04.937 --> 02:25:07.529
Yes, the Senate counts
for nothing anymore.

1126
02:25:07.629 --> 02:25:09.107
No one is safe from him.

1127
02:25:09.227 --> 02:25:10.607
He's a tyrant.

1128
02:25:10.727 --> 02:25:12.321
Then what can we do?

1129
02:25:12.421 --> 02:25:14.482
There's only one solution.

1130
02:25:15.919 --> 02:25:18.648
- If Caligula were to die...
- It could happen.

1131
02:26:21.919 --> 02:26:23.324
You need sleep.

1132
02:26:24.257 --> 02:26:27.781
I think I shall have to resign
myself to living forever.

1133
02:26:29.146 --> 02:26:30.660
I hope you do.

1134
02:26:48.988 --> 02:26:50.398
I am going bald.

1135
02:26:54.586 --> 02:26:55.952
No, you're not.

1136
02:26:56.497 --> 02:26:59.013
You've never been able
to face the facts, have you?

1137
02:26:59.602 --> 02:27:00.744
The facts?

1138
02:27:01.577 --> 02:27:03.091
Yes, my lord.

1139
02:27:03.836 --> 02:27:04.989
Can you?

1140
02:27:13.125 --> 02:27:16.111
I need some sleep.

1141
02:27:19.701 --> 02:27:21.197
I need you.

1142
02:27:50.073 --> 02:27:51.238
Are you ready?

1143
02:27:51.870 --> 02:27:54.737
Will you speak
your lying sister Isis?

1144
02:27:57.059 --> 02:28:01.605
Long have I wandered
in the land of men

1145
02:28:01.685 --> 02:28:05.241
in search of you, brother Osiris.

1146
02:28:12.782 --> 02:28:16.739
I have been killed
and cut in two bits.

1147
02:28:18.848 --> 02:28:24.818
You put my pieces together,
bringing back life...

1148
02:28:25.444 --> 02:28:26.607
with a kiss.

1149
02:28:29.185 --> 02:28:30.732
There goes our blood.

1150
02:28:35.018 --> 02:28:38.859
It doesn't matter.
It's only a show.

1151
02:28:49.789 --> 02:28:53.039
- I can't get it right.
- No, Caesar. Look, like that.

1152
02:28:57.838 --> 02:28:59.059
Hello, precious.

1153
02:29:03.945 --> 02:29:05.315
Have you been a good girl?

1154
02:29:13.543 --> 02:29:15.980
Don't you think she looks
beautiful in my costume?

1155
02:29:16.080 --> 02:29:18.163
- She's even wearing my little boots.
- Cause you like her power.

1156
02:29:18.243 --> 02:29:20.887
My little... boots.

1157
02:29:44.733 --> 02:29:46.080
She's serious.

1158
02:29:52.493 --> 02:29:54.340
Going to be dressed
like you today.

1159
02:30:24.943 --> 02:30:25.648
Password?

1160
02:30:27.937 --> 02:30:28.945
Scrotum.

1161
02:30:29.025 --> 02:30:30.148
So be it.

1162
02:31:14.177 --> 02:31:15.148
I'll...

1163
02:31:16.421 --> 02:31:17.413
live...

1164
02:31:19.281 --> 02:31:20.390
live...

1165
02:32:15.703 --> 02:32:16.686
Guards!

1166
02:32:20.695 --> 02:32:23.176
Hail, Claudius Caesar!

1167
02:32:23.256 --> 02:32:25.732
- Hail, Claudius Caesar!
- Hail, Claudius!

